list.abstract: BREAKFAST[ˈbrekfəst]，英语单词。作名词时，意为早饭。作动词时，意为吃早饭，进早餐。常见短语为have breakfast（吃早饭）。例句：We should have breakfast every day to keep healthy.（我们应该每天吃早餐以保持健康。） BREAKFAST作名词时近义词有dejeuner。

yingyinNormal.en: I thought breakfast was ready.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还以为早餐准备好了。

yingyinNormal.en: Pop-Tarts and Yoo-hoo. Breakfast of champions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 果馅饼和饼干。冠军专用早餐。

yingyinNormal.en: Morning. Morning. You're making eggs for breakfast?
yingyinNormal.zh: 早。今天早餐你做鸡蛋吃？

yingyinNormal.en: Good morning, miss. What can we bring you for breakfast?
yingyinNormal.zh: 早安，小姐，早餐想吃点什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Fine, whatever. Priya will be having breakfast.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，随你怎么说，那普丽娅就吃早餐好了。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, I made $17 before breakfast, what have you done?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我早餐前就赚了十七块耶，那你做了什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Here I come. Mummy Pig has finished her birthday breakfast.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我来咯。猪妈妈吃完了她的生日早餐。

yingyinNormal.en: Here I come. Mummy Pig has finished her birthday breakfast.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我来咯。猪妈妈吃完了她的生日早餐。

yingyinNormal.en: It's very simple. For breakfast, she has an egg-white Frittata.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很简单，早餐她要吃蛋白菜肉馅煎饼。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I had breakfast here so technically I saved $3.50.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我早餐在这个地方吃的，所以理论上我省了三块五。

yingyinNormal.en: So enjoy. Smoked oyster casserole with a breakfast-cereal crust.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么...尽情享受吧。熏牡蛎卷拌早餐麦片。

yingyinNormal.en: We brought food. Lox and bagels, the breakfast of time-travelers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们带了吃的熏鲑鱼和硬面包圈，时间旅人的早餐。

yingyinNormal.en: We're the non-judging breakfast club. We're your best friends.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们是"非指责早餐俱乐部"成员，我们是你最好的朋友。

yingyinNormal.en: This isn't breakfast, it's an experiment. 'Cause it looks a lot like breakfast.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不是早餐，这是试验。但看起来很像早餐。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy Pig and Daddy Pig have just made breakfast for Peppa and George. Breakfast is ready.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪妈妈和猪爸爸刚给佩琪和乔治做好早餐。早餐都做好啦。

yingyinNormal.en: It's fun having carrots for breakfast, mummy rabbit. Yes, we always have carrots for breakfast.
yingyinNormal.zh: 早餐吃胡萝卜真好玩，兔妈妈。是的，我们早餐一直吃胡萝卜。

yingyinNormal.en: Mom thinks we're shopping. I told Dad I was making us breakfast. When have you ever made us breakfast?
yingyinNormal.zh: 老妈以为我们在逛街。我跟老爸说我在给我们做早餐。你什么时候给我们做过早餐了？

yingyinNormal.en: Not one cereal mascot is a girl. It's a total breakfast sausage fest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所有谷类早餐吉祥物都是男生，谷物早餐界完全"基肠""露露"啊。

yingyinNormal.en: You never know. That's why I ordered us breakfast from the fancy breakfast place on the corner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 世事无常啊，所以我的早餐都是在街角那家高级餐厅订的。

yingyinNormal.en: It's fun having carrots for breakfast, Mummy Rabbit. Yes, we always have carrots for breakfast. I could eat carrots all day, but I'd better go to work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 早餐的时候吃胡萝卜这真是一件有趣的事呢兔妈妈。是啊，我们每天早餐吃的都是胡萝卜。我可以吃一整天胡萝卜，但是我得去上班了。

word_usage.usage:
通常在一日三餐breakfast，lunch，supper前不加a或the。
示例：先生，早饭准备好了。
误 The breakfast is ready, sir.
正 Breakfast is ready, sir.

have breakfast表示吃早饭，通常只用主动形式，不可用于被动。
示例：那天是8点钟吃的早饭。
误 Breakfast was had at eight o'clock that day.
正 We had breakfast at eight o'clock that day.

examination_example.sentence: Another, funded by Quaker Oats, concluded, as a Daily Mail story put it, that "hot oatmeal (燕麦粥) <highlight>breakfast</highlight> keeps you full for longer."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 另一个由Quaker Oats资助的项目得出结论，正如《每日邮报》的一篇报道所说，“热燕麦粥早餐能让你更长时间保持饱腹感。”

examination_example.sentence: If asked, most people will be able to give a vague description of their main meals: <highlight>breakfast</highlight>, lunch, dinner.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果被问到这个问题，大多数人都能大致描述一下他们的主食：早餐、午餐、晚餐。

examination_example.sentence: But whether it's an English-cooked <highlight>breakfast</highlight> or a coffee and a sandwich, one thing has remained the same: the prices.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但无论是英式早餐还是咖啡配三明治，有一点是不会变的：价格。
